Request to have all the field shows in the email.

As per quoted from one of my customer:
{quote}
When we build a custom workflow, one of the things we can add to a transition is a post function. Currently there are many to choose from but a useful one would be for the person to whom the case gets assigned in that transition, to receive - not just the most recent comment - but a full transcript of the case including all fields (like the emails received when the case is first opened) and all comments.

Effectively this is like the view you see of the case, when you view it online - only this time you're receiving it in an email automatically as part of a workflow step.
{quote}

For example: When we comment one particular issue, the notification/email will be sent to any related user to that particular issue. And the email only shows the comment only, without showing all the fields and including all the comments that has been commented from that particular issue.

Related issue: [JST-126664|https://support.atlassian.com/browse/JST-126664]

