Considering Text Gadget is the only text-display gadget that can be individually customized (compared to Introduction gadget and Announcement Banner), and that it is a very useful for customers not only in Cloud side as raised [here JRA-29848|https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRA-29848] but also for JIRA Server, perhaps we could have a better approach for this. Maybe using the wiki-style renderer or even a plain text.

